SUPPORT COMMUNICATION - SECURITY BULLETIN

Document ID: c04790231
Version: 1

HPSBGN03504 rev.1 - HP UCMDB, Local Disclosure of Sensitive Information

NOTICE: The information in this Security Bulletin should be acted upon as
soon as possible.

Release Date: 2015-09-09
Last Updated: 2015-09-09

Potential Security Impact: Disclosure of Sensitive Information

Source: Hewlett-Packard Company, HP Software Security Response Team

VULNERABILITY SUMMARY
Potential security vulnerabilities have been identified in HP UCMDB which
would allow local disclosure of sensitive information.

References:

CVE-2015-5440
SSRT102237

SUPPORTED SOFTWARE VERSIONS*: ONLY impacted versions are listed.
HP UCMDB v10.00, v10.01, v10.10, v10.11, v10.20

BACKGROUND

CVSS 2.0 Base Metrics
===========================================================
  Reference              Base Vector             Base Score
CVE-2015-5440    (AV:L/AC:L/Au:N/C:C/I:C/A:C)       7.2
===========================================================
             Information on CVSS is documented
            in HP Customer Notice: HPSN-2008-002

RESOLUTION

HP has made the following instructions available to resolve the vulnerability
in HP UCMDB, HP UCMDB Configuration Manager, HP UCMDB Browser, and HP
Universal Discovery:

For versions v10.0 and v10.01 use Patch Version - UCMDB 10.01CUP12:

Windows - https://softwaresupport.hp.com/group/softwaresupport/search-result/
- -/facetsearch/document/LID/UCMDB_00169

Linux - https://softwaresupport.hp.com/group/softwaresupport/search-result/-/
facetsearch/document/LID/UCMDB_00170

For versions v10.10 and v10.11 Patch Version - UCMDB 10.11CUP6:

Windows - https://softwaresupport.hp.com/group/softwaresupport/search-result/
- -/facetsearch/document/LID/UCMDB_00167

Linux - https://softwaresupport.hp.com/group/softwaresupport/search-result/-/
facetsearch/document/LID/UCMDB_00168

For version v10.20 use Patch Version - UCMDB10.21:

Windows - https://softwaresupport.hp.com/group/softwaresupport/search-result/
- -/facetsearch/document/LID/UCMDB_00163

Linux - https://softwaresupport.hp.com/group/softwaresupport/search-result/-/
facetsearch/document/LID/UCMDB_00164

